szakacs.kpi.fei.tuke.intrfc.arena.game.gameLevel

Interface GameLevelPrivileged

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GameLevelBasic, GameLevelUpdatable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TreasureScooperLevel

    public interface GameLevelPrivileged
extends GameLevelUpdatable
    An extension to the GameLevelUpdatable interface that is exposed to the core backend classes managing the game logic as well as any classes external to the game logic.
